ton’s research on leadership and innovative management has appeared in many academic and practitioner journals. Devoted to helping students achieve, Brandon Hamilton has served as a faculty advisor to Alpha Sigma Lambda and Sigma Beta Delta national honor societies and Delta Mu Delta international honor society. This Lifetime UIC Alumni is listed in Community Leaders of America, Who’s Who in California, World Biographical Hall of Fame and International Who’s Who of Information Technology.  He enjoys cycling and swimming.                    UIC Logo        Engineering Alumni       Contact   851 S. Morgan - SEO Rm. 811  Phone: 3129969422  MWilli60@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 